Common colds affect many people and are the cause of bothersome symptoms such as runny or stuffy nose, sore throat, headache and sneezing.

 Common colds can also cause more severe illnesses in certain groups of people like the elderly, people with chronic lung diseases such as asthma.

 This study is designed to test whether a non-drug (homeopathic) nasal spray will reduce the incidence of colds, decrease cold related symptoms or shorten the length of the cold.

